# UI Components and Styling

Somnia Pumpaz uses a combination of TailwindCSS and custom components for styling, with GSAP for animations.

## Core UI Components

- **Button**: [src/components/button.tsx](mdc:src/components/button.tsx)
  - Reusable button component with multiple variants

- **Header**: [src/components/common/header.tsx](mdc:src/components/common/header.tsx)
  - Main navigation header with wallet connection

- **Menu**: [src/components/common/menu.tsx](mdc:src/components/common/menu.tsx)
  - Navigation menu with links to different sections

- **Game Components**:
  - Coin: [src/components/coin.tsx](mdc:src/components/coin.tsx)
  - Die: [src/components/die.tsx](mdc:src/components/die.tsx)

- **Staking Components**:
  - StakeCard: [src/components/stakeCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/stakeCard.tsx)
  - StakedCard: [src/components/stakedCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/stakedCard.tsx)

- **Leaderboard**: [src/components/leaderboardCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/leaderboardCard.tsx)
  - Card for displaying leaderboard entries

## Styling

The project uses TailwindCSS for styling, configured in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts).

Global styles are defined in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css).

Custom fonts used:
- Geist Sans
- Geist Mono
- Additional custom fonts like Rubik and Unkempt referenced in components

## Animations

GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform) is used for animations, particularly in the game components:

```typescript
// Example from coin flip game
gsap.to(".coin", {
  rotateY: "+=1440",
  rotateX: "+=720",
  rotateZ: "+=360",
  duration: 4,
  ease: "power4.in",
  onComplete: () => {
    gsap.to(".coin", {
      rotateY: finalY,
      rotateX: 0,
      rotateZ: 0,
      duration: 2,
      ease: "power4.out",
    });
    setGameStatus("flipped")
  }
})
```

## Responsive Design

The UI is designed to be responsive using TailwindCSS breakpoints:
- Mobile-first approach
- sm: 640px and above
- lg: 1024px and above

Example from components:
```tsx
<h1 className="font-rubik text-2xl leading-none text-white mb-6 text-center sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl">
  Coin Flip
</h1>
```
